.TH "LIGHTNING-NODE-LISTFORWARDS-OUT-MSAT-SKEWNESS" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-node-listforwards-out-msat-skewness \- FEAT-2829 node-listforwards-out-msat-skewness
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning node-listforwards-out-msat-skewness
.SH DESCRIPTION
Computes skewness of outgoing msat values across settled forwards (FEAT-2829).
.PP
Output: JSON from CLN.
.TP
.B out_msat_skewness
Fisher-Pearson skewness of out_msat values from settled forwards.
.TP
.B n
Number of data points used.
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning(1)
